    <div class="reveal">
    <h2>What Is Technical SEO</h2>

    <p>Technical SEO encompasses every aspect of your website that influences how search engines crawl, render, index, and rank your pages. It breaks down into six core components:</p>

    <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-3 gap-5 not-prose my-8">
