    <p>If your website is not ranking where it ought to, the root cause is often technical rather than creative. Guildford businesses operating in competitive Surrey markets cannot afford to let technical debt accumulate unchecked. <a href="/free-seo-audit-guildford/">A free SEO audit</a> is a lower-commitment starting point, and full <a href="/seo-pricing-guildford/">technical SEO pricing</a> is set out separately for businesses ready to scope a project.</p>
